rcel.com/changelog\">Changelog</a></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-module__0CIgbq__cell hero-module__0CIgbq__titleCell\" data-grid-cell=\"\" style=\"--sm-grid-row:2 / span 1;--sm-grid-column:1/-1;--sm-cell-rows:1;--sm-cell-columns:-2;padding:0\">\n         <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-initial\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-module__0CIgbq__cell hero-module__0CIgbq__authorCell\" data-grid-cell=\"\" style=\"--sm-grid-row:3 / span 1;--sm-grid-column:1/-1;--sm-cell-rows:1;--sm-cell-columns:-2;padding:0\">\n         <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center w-full relative\">\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-initial\">\n           <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-2 flex-initial hero-module__0CIgbq__fewAuthorsContainer\">\n            <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mehulkar\" rel=\"author\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline hero-module__0CIgbq__author\"> \n             <div class=\"flex flex-row items-stretch justify-start gap-2 flex-initial hero-module__0CIgbq__authorStack\">\n              <span class=\"text-[14px] leading-[20px] font-medium text-gray-1000 hero-module__0CIgbq__name\">Mehul Kar</span><span class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900 hero-module__0CIgbq__role\">Software Engineer</span>\n             </div> \n            </a><a href=\"https://github.com/ShayCichocki\" rel=\"author\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline hero-module__0CIgbq__author\"> \n             <div class=\"flex flex-row items-stretch justify-start gap-2 flex-initial hero-module__0CIgbq__authorStack\">\n              <span class=\"text-[14px] leading-[20px] font-medium text-gray-1000 hero-module__0CIgbq__name\">Shay Cichocki</span><span class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900 hero-module__0CIgbq__role\">Software Engineer</span>\n             </div> \n            </a>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </section>\n       <div class=\"article-module__XJFYTq__topGap\" data-grid=\"\" style=\"--grid-rows:1;--sm-grid-columns:2;--lg-grid-columns:3;--sm-height:var(--grid-divider-gap);border-bottom:none\"></div>\n       <main data-grid=\"\" style=\"--sm-grid-rows:2;--lg-grid-rows:1;--sm-grid-columns:2;--lg-grid-columns:3;--sm-height:fit-content;border-bottom:none\">\n        <article class=\"article-module__XJFYTq__articleContent\" data-grid-cell=\"\" style=\"--sm-grid-row:1 / span 1;--sm-grid-column:1/3;--lg-grid-column:1/4;--sm-cell-rows:1;--sm-cell-columns:2;--lg-cell-columns:3\">\n         <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__XJFYTq__content\">\n          <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-between flex-initial w-full gap-4 pt-2\">\n           <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-start gap-1.5 flex-initial\">\n            <p class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900\">1<!-- --> min <!-- -->read</p>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-6 flex-1 justify-start\"></div>\n           <time class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900 order-2 md:order-3\" datetime=\"2026-05-18T15:42-05:00\">May 18, 2026</time>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"rounded-md! p-2! bg-background-100! shadow-[var(--ds-shadow-border-small)]! bg-clip-padding! max-w-[900px]! grid! sm:border-l-0! sm:border-r-0! sm:border-(--guide-color)! sm:w-full! mt-4 mb-6 max-w-(--article-max-width)\">\n           <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"[.dark-theme_&amp;]:hidden! h-auto max-w-full rounded-sm border border-solid border-gray-200\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F7wzza5neuEZJ9buQ1IYSR4%2F1582a8ac567be74d6ff83ad899dd1560%2Fconsolidated-commit-light.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F7wzza5neuEZJ9buQ1IYSR4%2F1582a8ac567be74d6ff83ad899dd1560%2Fconsolidated-commit-light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F7wzza5neuEZJ9buQ1IYSR4%2F1582a8ac567be74d6ff83ad899dd1560%2Fconsolidated-commit-light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"><img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"[.light-theme_&amp;]:hidden! h-auto max-w-full rounded-sm border border-solid border-gray-200\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5Sn58NCNkunsu16GPGUORF%2Fb0540391ae3d35574e5509111705032a%2Fconsolidated-commit-dark.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5Sn58NCNkunsu16GPGUORF%2Fb0540391ae3d35574e5509111705032a%2Fconsolidated-commit-dark.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5Sn58NCNkunsu16GPGUORF%2Fb0540391ae3d35574e5509111705032a%2Fconsolidated-commit-dark.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Monorepos can now opt in to a single, consolidated commit status on pull requests instead of one commit status per project. For repos with many projects, teams can configure GitHub branch protection once, then manage which Vercel projects are required for merge in each project’s settings.</p>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Read more about <a href=\"https://vercel-docs-git-docs-gh-commit-status.vercel.sh/docs/git/vercel-for-github#commit-status\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel-docs-git-docs-gh-commit-status.vercel.sh/docs/git/vercel-for-github#commit-status\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Github Commit statuses</a> and and enable Consolidated Commit Status from your <a href=\"https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%5Bproject%5D%2Fsettings%2Fgit%23git-commits\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%5Bproject%5D%2Fsettings%2Fgit%23git-commits\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">project settings</a>.</p>\n         </div>\n        </article>\n       </main>\n       <div data-grid=\"\" style=\"--grid-rows:1;--sm-grid-columns:2;--lg-grid-columns:3;--sm-height:var(--grid-divider-gap)\"></div>\n       <section data-grid=\"\" style=\"--sm-grid-rows:2;--lg-grid-rows:1;--sm-grid-columns:2;--lg-grid-columns:3;--sm-height:fit-content\">\n        <div class=\"footer-module__QGSwJW__primaryCell\" data-grid-cell=\"\" style=\"--sm-grid-row:1 / span 1;--sm-grid-column:1/3;--sm-cell-rows:1;--sm-cell-columns:2\">\n         <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start justify-center gap-6 flex-initial\">\n          <div class=\"footer-module__QGSwJW__primaryDescription\">\n           <p><b>Ready to deploy? </b>Start building with a free account. Speak to an expert for your <i>Pro</i> or <u>Enterprise</u> needs.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-row items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial undefined\">\n           <a role=\"link\" href=\"https://vercel.com/new\" type=\"submit\" tabindex=\"0\" data-react-aria-pressable=\"true\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-intent=\"Get Started\" data-zone=\"2d9dc9\" class=\"button-module__QyrFCa__base reset-module__ylizOa__reset button-module__QyrFCa__button geist-new-themed geist-new-default geist-new-default-fill button-module__QyrFCa__rounded button-module__QyrFCa__invert\" data-geist-button=\"\" data-prefix=\"false\" data-suffix=\"false\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--geist-icon-size:16px\"><span class=\"button-module__QyrFCa__content\"> \n             <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-start gap-2 flex-initial\">Start Deploying</div> \n            </span></a><a role=\"link\" type=\"submit\" tabindex=\"0\" data-react-aria-pressable=\"true\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-intent=\"Contact Sales\" data-zone=\"same\" class=\"button-module__QyrFCa__base reset-module__ylizOa__reset button-module__QyrFCa__button button-module__QyrFCa__secondary button-module__QyrFCa__rounded button-module__QyrFCa__shadow button-module__QyrFCa__invert\" data-geist-button=\"\" data-prefix=\"false\" data-suffix=\"false\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--geist-icon-size:16px\" href=\"https://vercel.com/contact/sales\"><span class=\"button-module__QyrFCa__content\"> \n             <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-start gap-2 flex-initial\">Talk to an Expert</div> \n            </span></a>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer-module__QGSwJW__secondaryCell footer-module__QGSwJW__secondaryCellRenderingCTAAsButton\" data-grid-cell=\"\" style=\"--sm-grid-row:2 / span 1;--lg-grid-row:1 / span 1;--sm-grid-column:1/3;--lg-grid-column:3/4;--sm-cell-rows:1;--sm-cell-columns:2;--lg-cell-columns:1;overflow:visible\">\n         <div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-col items-center lg:items-start justify-center gap-4 lg:gap-6 flex-initial\">\n          <div class=\"footer-module__QGSwJW__secondaryDescription\">\n           <p><b>Explore Vercel Enterprise</b> with an interactive product tour, trial, or a personalized demo.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-center lg:justify-between gap-6 lg:gap-2 flex-initial\">\n           <a role=\"link\" type=\"submit\" tabindex=\"0\" data-react-aria-pressable=\"true\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-intent=\"Contact Sales\" data-zone=\"same\" class=\"button-module__QyrFCa__base reset-module__ylizOa__reset button-module__QyrFCa__button button-module__QyrFCa__secondary button-module__QyrFCa__rounded button-module__QyrFCa__shadow button-module__QyrFCa__invert\" data-geist-button=\"\" data-prefix=\"false\" data-suffix=\"false\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--geist-icon-size:16px\" href=\"https://vercel.com/try-enterprise\"><span class=\"button-module__QyrFCa__content\"> \n             <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-start gap-2 flex-initial\">Explore Enterprise</div> \n            </span></a>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-grid-cross=\"\" style=\"--cross-row:1;--cross-column:1\"></div>\n        <div data-grid-cross=\"\" style=\"transform:translateY(1px);--sm-cross-row:3;--lg-cross-row:2;--cross-column:-1\"></div>\n       </section>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--$-->\n    <!--/$-->\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <!--$-->\n  <!--/$-->\n  <!--$-->\n  <!--$-->\n  <!--/$-->\n  <!--$-->\n  <!--/$-->\n  <!--/$-->\n  <!--$-->\n  <!--/$-->\n  <!--$-->\n  <!--/$-->\n  <!--$-->\n  <!--/$-->\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 现在为 GitHub 拉取请求上的单体仓库提供统一的提交状态，简化了分支保护配置。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 现在为 GitHub 拉取请求上的单体仓库提供统一的提交状态，简化了分支保护配置。",
  "summary": "Vercel 的这篇更新日志宣布了一项针对单体仓库的新功能：在 GitHub 拉取请求上提供单一的、统一的提交状态，取代了之前每个项目一个状态的模式。这简化了 GitHub 中的分支保护配置，团队可以一次性定义保护规则，并从各个项目设置中管理哪些 Vercel 项目是合并所必需的。该功能为可选启用，可在项目设置中找到。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vercel 为 GitHub 上的单体仓库引入了统一的提交状态。",
      "explanation": "单体仓库现在可以选择在拉取请求上使用单一的、统一的提交状态，而不是每个项目一个提交状态，从而减少噪音并简化分支保护配置。"
    },
    {
      "point": "简化了拥有多个项目的单体仓库的 GitHub 分支保护。",
      "explanation": "团队可以在 GitHub 中一次性配置分支保护规则，然后从每个项目的设置中管理哪些特定的 Vercel 项目是合并所必需的，从而提高工作流效率。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "单体仓库现在可以选择在拉取请求上使用单一的、统一的提交状态，而不是每个项目一个提交状态。",
    "对于拥有多个项目的仓库，团队可以一次性配置 GitHub 分支保护，然后在每个项目的设置中管理哪些 Vercel 项目是合并所必需的。"
  ],
